messages.message:
If you're not modifying .proto or .thrift files in your PR, use SKIP_PYGEN=true for faster builds!

Usage:
make build mypy SKIP_PYGEN=true
make build runlocal SKIP_PYGEN=true
make run-test-local SKIP_PYGEN=true

https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/8682

works really nicely when you just want to modify or mypy one Python file, example:

make build mypy SKIP_PYGEN=true NAME=instabase/ocr/server/libs/ocr_parse.py
